title: [PARODY]Captain America Parody
description:
Description:Captain America Parody: Collector`s 2-Disc Edition. CAPTAIN AMERICA XXX picks up 70 years after Steve Rogers, codename: Captain America, single handedly ended World War II. Thawed from a block of ice, Rogers (Evan Stone) is back, and he`s the only thing standing between America and the forces of evil. Along with Nick Fury(Sean Michaels), Sharon Carter (Tara Lynn Foxx) and the rest of top-secret organization S.H.I.E.L.D., Cap has to battle his arch nemesis, The Red Skull (Bill Bailey). There`s also the sexy-but-deadly Madame HYDRA (Juelz Ventura), who wants to ride him as badly as she wants to kill him! Leaked government files led to CAPTAIN AMERICA XXX, where private citizens may witness the red-blooded hero bone and battle his way through the modern era.Jennifer White takes on the role of Betsy Ross, while Dane Cross plays Dr. Bruce Banner. The movie also stars adult sensations India Summer, Charley Chase, Jacky Joy, Ashley Orion, Lizzy Borden, Scott Lyons and Alec Knight. The politics have changed, but the sex remains the same!
